{
  "texts": [
    "The results of LSTM and GPT models on the same tasks are reported for comparison.",
    "Each model was trained on 1.9M SMILES strings from ChEMBL and used to generate 102,400 SMILES strings de novo.",
    "The number and percentage of valid, unique, and novel molecular designs are reported.",
    "The best value per metric is highlighted in boldface.",
    "Nature Communications | (2024) 15:6176"
  ]
}